<h2>The form target attribute</h2>
<p>When submitting this form, the result will be opened in a new browser tab:</p>
<form action="/action_page.php" target="_blank">
  <label for="fname">Họ:</label><br>
  <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" value="Hoàng Đức"><br>
  <label for="lname">Tên:</label><br>
  <input type="text" id="lname" name="lname" value="Thịnh"><br><br>
  <input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form> 
</body>
